NAME
     StorageDEHelper -- Helper daemon for storage statistics

SYNOPSIS
     StorageDEHelper

DESCRIPTION
     StorageDEHelper is a helper daemon which uses applessdstatistics to
     gather statistics related to the internal storage device.

